snippet.title: Diana plays with  Kindi Kids dolls
snippet.description:
This is a paid ad for Kindi Kids from Moose Toys. Parents, the Kindi Kids animated show is available to watch on YouTube, here: https://bit.ly/3hZ0vYm

Diana plays with Kindi Kids dolls: Mysta Bella, Marsha Mello, Donatina, Cindy Pops, Summer Peaches. They paint together, change dresses, treat a cat and play outside.

Subscribe to Kids Diana Show - http://bit.ly/2k7NrSx
https://www.instagram.com/kidsdianashow/ Facebook https://www.facebook.com/KidsDianaShowOfficial/
